headline: J. M. Smucker Q3 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: J. M. Smucker (NYSE:SJM) reported fiscal 2026 third-quarter results that management said exceeded internal expectations, supported by strong comparable net sales growth and continued demand for key brands, while profitability was pressured by higher costs and a sharp decline in the Sweet Baked Snack
